{"tid":790850,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"英特爾修改微碼使用條款：禁止進行“patch”前後性能對比","createTime":"2018-08-23T10:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:30:17.000Z","uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a97ab06d8f5c3f3b4a3df7e2b838550e8774ed2e","tid":790850,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"Much of the secret sauce that made Intel processors faster than AMD is going sour, as the cybersecurity community is finding gaping security vulnerabilities by exploiting features such as speculative execution. Intel's microcode updates that mitigate these vulnerabilities impact performance. Intel isn't too happy about public performance numbers put out by its customers, which it fears could blunt the competitive edge of its products. The company has hence updated the license terms governing the microcode update distribution to explicitly forbid its users from publishing comparative &quot;before/after&quot; performance numbers of patched processors. <br />\n<br />\nThe updated license for the microcode update has this controversial sentence (pay attention to &quot;v&quot;):<br />\n<br />\n&quot;You will not, and will not allow any third party to (i) use, copy, distribute, sell or offer to sell the Software or associated documentation; (ii) modify, adapt, enhance, disassemble, decompile, reverse engineer, change or create derivative works from the Software except and only to the extent as specifically required by mandatory applicable laws or any applicable third party license terms accompanying the Software; (iii) use or make the Software available for the use or benefit of third parties; or (iv) use the Software on Your products other than those that include the Intel hardware product(s), platform(s), or software identified in the Software;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> or (v) publish or provide any Software benchmark or comparison test results.&quot;<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSome of Intel's biggest enterprise customers are cloud computing providers such as AWS, Microsoft, and Google, who have made it their duty to keep their customers informed about the performance impact of microcode updated processors, since it impacts their cost/performance when the scale is big enough. This gag is both unethical, and probably even illegal. <br />\n<br />\nSource link: <a href=\"https://www.techpowerup.com/247028/intel-gags-customers-from-publishing-performance-impact-of-microcode-updates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techpowerup.com%2F247028%2Fintel-gags-customers-from-publishing-performance-impact-of-microcode-updates&d=4KOIsct425NuqQAI0zM6%2FW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f8c19898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techpowerup.com/247028/intel-gags-customers-from-publishing-performance-impact-of-microcode-updates</a>"},{"pid":"6a95a0b631f43309caefdc207792e21e066b3942","tid":790850,"uid":32577,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁大間公司做埋啲咁柒既野"},{"pid":"ba56b449c4170dc8d7b72420a0ebd02e4ca4c7b4","tid":790850,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199e7657e56c7c0bf3ca1d256f500e8da96a8380","tid":790850,"uid":15495,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩公司，下部砌ryzen"},{"pid":"c69f14e932c0d02fe73fcc817b7244abd635fb7b","tid":790850,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Fuck you Intel</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7cb14bfc157b70a52b086f58679337ed7eaa02","tid":790850,"uid":48362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"自從當年佢出新u就要換底板開始<br />\n已經覺得佢無得救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c2935d0594a7597fc115b4a698dd554bd05904","tid":790850,"uid":76705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"等ram平返砌2700x<br />\nIntel都on撚9"},{"pid":"1fbca2a2555aaa35446578a722bef138a46dba4a","tid":790850,"uid":6381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001cfd1fa71fd8946c83e3be8f5dcecfff64d12d","tid":790850,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"Intel係咪痴撚左線？<br />\n<br />\n光明正大開出黎你都仲可以用光明正大既方法兜<br />\n<br />\n全部消息轉往暗處散播你點兜？"},{"pid":"1301c695da81e185e731d91ecfe6f11975fddb8e","tid":790850,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>updated</strong></span> : <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">果條條款已移除</span>"},{"pid":"3df3e71d6a41d6f32b07761ca9c1907cc0c62d8f","tid":790850,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1301c695da81e185e731d91ecfe6f11975fddb8e","tid":790850,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>updated</strong></span> : <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">果條條款已移除</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.techpowerup.com/247050/intel-updates-microcode-license-deleting-no-benchmarks-clause\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techpowerup.com%2F247050%2Finte